org.hibernate.dialect.aggregate.AggregateSupport

Packages that use AggregateSupport
Package
Description
org.hibernate.dialect
This package abstracts over the multifarious dialects of SQL understood by the databases supported by Hibernate.
org.hibernate.dialect.aggregate
Support for Dialect-specific aggregate column types, including user-defined composite types, and JSON or XML types.
